## 5. React Query — Query Keys

**`src/hooks/queries/queryKeys.ts`** — Central key registry.

```ts
myEntity: {
  all: ["myEntity"] as const,
  lists: () => [...queryKeys.myEntity.all, "list"] as const,
  detail: (id: number) => [...queryKeys.myEntity.all, "detail", id] as const,
},
```

Existing keys: `accounts`, `accountsPaginated`, `channels`, `campaigns`, `assets`, `googleConversionActions`, `googleProfiles`

